name: Blake Elly
description: Hello there i am Blake a single parent of one. i am a gentle man, love the good things of life and love to live life to the fullest i would like to meet my Soul mate, a woman with a good heat. I am reasonably new on social network i ended up here purely by accident via a link.i work as an independent contractor of international repute..I love meeting people.. being Single is lonely’ i like cooking, reading, hang-out with My family and love ones,looking forward in meeting a companion..
